{"tid":2396954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華試驗反導彈攔截 美艦入西沙群島","createTime":"2021-02-06T04:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T04:47:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf378fe8fb8e115535c0ae68989b48366353c00a","tid":2396954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/BESD5Z63VJGIRBMBIZZXBICLXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FBESD5Z63VJGIRBMBIZZXBICLXY%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=0d9ac136\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FBESD5Z63VJGIRBMBIZZXBICLXY%2F&h=21c27faa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/BESD5Z63VJGIRBMBIZZXBICLXY/</a><br />\n<br />\n華試驗反導彈攔截 美艦入西沙群島<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美雙方軍事動作頻繁。美軍導彈驅逐艦「麥凱恩號」前天穿越台灣海峽後，中國國防部同日深夜稱，當日在境內進行一次陸基中段反導攔截試驗。中方强調試驗屬防禦性，不針對任何國家。翌日，早前在台海現身的「麥凱恩號」再進入南海西沙群島水域。解放軍表示，南部戰區組織海空兵力跟蹤監視，並予以警告驅離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FHvuIxnJhLfh_JC1MEUCOu4fenw=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QNIVMGHBJRFI3H6NYAVWL7EHJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFHvuIxnJhLfh_JC1MEUCOu4fenw%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQNIVMGHBJRFI3H6NYAVWL7EHJU.jpg&h=8e7016c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美「麥凱恩號」驅逐艦穿越台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「即日試驗」做法罕見<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部僅用61個字通報，指前日在境內進行一次陸基中段反導攔截技術試驗，達到預期目的。然而這則通報「字少事大」，具新華社背景的微信公眾號「牛彈琴」形容，今次試驗是對美軍示警。YouTube「軍武器研」頻道主持Larry對本報稱，中國自2010年至今已進行五次試驗，過往試驗有時間表，不會即興為之，今次「即日進行，即日公佈」做法罕見，不排除是對美軍導彈驅逐艦通過台海，及美軍戰略司令部的核戰言論作回應。<br />\n<br />\n事態於翌日升級，美軍驅逐艦「麥凱恩號」（USS John S. McCain DDG-56）行經台灣海峽後，。。一。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n南海局勢近日緊張，美國防部早。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6e5cbb858f5d834c52d18a1647df4139124dd964","tid":2396954,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"拜登：皇上第七艦隊將入台平定台灣亂黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}